This paper deals with natural language processing and deep learning models for semantic representation, which are typically covered under the sub-category of "Computation and Language" (cs.CL). The paper also involves training neural networks, which falls under "Machine Learning" (cs.LG) and "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions evaluations of the proposed method using image captioning, which can be related to "Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition" (cs.CV).
